snippet.title: Amber Heard Tells Johnny Depp He Won't Be Believed Because He's A Man
snippet.description:
Another video on the Amber Heard - Johnny Depp case. It won't be the last, but at least not for a little while.

Sources:
https://www.small-screen.co.uk/aquaman-2-amber-heard-replaced-warner-bros-pictures-dc-comics/
https://www.thewrap.com/johnny-depp-is-being-blackmailed-by-amber-heard-heres-how-i-know-guest-column/
https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7966723/Amber-Heard-ridicules-Johnny-Depp-claiming-hes-domestic-violence-victim.html#reader-comments
https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2
Full details of the case can be found on Incredibly Average's channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ
